{
  "stem": "935.8",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I know I was pretty far in the back because I know when they walked me out, it was a long hallway.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Or perhaps it seemed long because I was not in very good shape.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But a long hallway.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they were in front, so that they could get them out fast.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That much, I know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I know that just in the last interrogation, a different man was sitting there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I still can't think of this name. it will come to me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was a different kommissar.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "A Dutch guy, a young, Dutch guy.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I thought, I can impress him by speaking Dutch.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He didn't care a bit about it, but I also noticed he was not very, very, very professional in what he did.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He was new in the job.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Totally new.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "The next thing-- it was three months I was down there-- we were evacuated from the bunker.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Out.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "The bunker was totally evacuated because, again, it was toward the end that they expected this camp to be taken over.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They wanted the political prisoners to be taken away and safe somewhere.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And Eva and I were sent back in the camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And when I came out, after three months, there were wall to wall-- or I should say, camp street to camp street of people lying, prisoners lying.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "There were 100,000 people from all the camps, which had been already evacuated.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Whoever could-- including Auschwitz, all the Hungarians from other camps-- they were walked, on trucks, whatever, to this one camp.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Nobody had room for them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Nobody had food for them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Nobody knew what was going on.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "They were just lying around on the street.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Or they were taken off the trucks, loaded on the trucks again, into a forest-- bang, bang, bang, bang.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
